snippet.title: Finnish Cabin Mayhem - EARLY GAMEPLAY TRAILER
snippet.description:
Upcoming Indie FPS game straight from the barren wasteland of eastern Finland.  Get drunk with your friends and kick their asses using a wide arsenal of random stuff.

Wishlist Finnish Cabin Mayhem on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3135990/Finnish_Cabin_Mayhem__Mokkimahina/
